data.description: Unleash your imagination in this 4+1 bedroom, 1+1 bathroom home that radiates potential! Upstairs, you'll find a cozy two-bedroom, one-bathroom retreat, perfect for your main living space. Venture downstairs to discover an additional three bedrooms and another bathroom, offering flexible living arrangements. Nestled close to the lake, entertainment hotspots, and recreation areas, this home is your gateway to year-round excitement and relaxation. Take advantage of this extraordinary chance to transform this space into your dream oasis!
